nhc_headline: ...GABRIELLE RACING EAST-NORTHEASTWARD ACROSS THE NORTH ATLANTIC... ...HURRICANE WARNING IN EFFECT FOR THE AZORES...
summary: ...GABRIELLE RACING EAST-NORTHEASTWARD ACROSS THE NORTH ATLANTIC... ...HURRICANE WARNING IN EFFECT FOR THE AZORES... As of 8:00 AM AST Wed Sep 24 the center of Gabrielle was located near 35.8, -50.2 with movement ENE at 25 mph. The minimum central pressure was 960 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 115 mph.
